<front>
<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Hans Maurer</head><p>Der Rat sendet zwei Glaubbriefe für Bischof Raban von Speyer und Pfalzgraf Ludwig III. wegen Verlängerung des Waffenstillstands mit den Herren von Hanau bis Weihnachten.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_158" id="78v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_158_r1l13">Hanſen <expan>Mawr<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_158_r1l14"><expan>Lıeb<ex>er</ex></expan> Hans / VVir <expan>ſchıcke<ex>n</ex></expan> dir beÿ diſem <expan>bot<ex>e</ex>n</expan> cʒwen gelawbſbriefe </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_158_r1l15">einen an <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>gnedıge<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> <expan>H<ex>er</ex>cʒog</expan> Ludwigen / vnd einen an <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_158_r1l16">von Speÿre / . was du <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan> an ſie werbſt <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> von </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_158_r1l18">Hanaw <expan>vvege<ex>n</ex></expan> / daʒ ſie dir 
<add><ab facs="#facs_158_r1l17">des </ab></add> <expan>gelawb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> etc . vnd <expan>diſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> brıef <expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_158_r1l19">Jn / vnd vvirb von <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan> / Als die ſtallung gen den von </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_158_r1l20">Hanaw / <expan>yecʒund<ex>en</ex></expan> auf ſant Mıchels tag awſgeet / . vnd bitt ſie </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_158_r1l21">daʒ ſie darcʒü beholffen ſein / daʒ dieſelb ſache <expan>leng<ex>er</ex></expan> beſtellet <expan>w<ex>er</ex>de</expan> / </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_158_r1l22">vnd ſo das ye <expan>leng<ex>er</ex></expan> geſein möcht ye 
<del rend="strikethrough"><expan>g<ex>er</ex></expan></del> peſſer vns dewchte / </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_158_r1l24">Möht es <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan> nicht 
<add><ab facs="#facs_158_line_1576584581077_4878">lenger </ab></add> geſein / daʒ es doch auf <expan>weihenacht<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_158_r1l25">ee auf ſant <expan>Mert<ex>ein</ex></expan> beſtellet würd / . vnd laʒʒ dir das <expan>beuolh<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_158_r1l26">ſein / Auch ſolt du danyden <expan>beleib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> bis <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> tag ein end nem / . </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_158" id="78v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Hansen <expan>Mawr<ex>er</ex></expan>
</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Lieb<ex>er</ex></expan> Hans, wir <expan>schicke<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        dir bey disem <expan>bot<ex>e</ex>n</expan> czwen gelawbsbriefe. Einen an
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnedige<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>, <expan>h<ex>er</ex>czog</expan> Ludwigen,
                        und einen an <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> von Speyre, was du
                            <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan> an sie werbst <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> von Hanaw <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan>, daz sie
                        dir <add>des</add>
<expan>gelawb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> etc. Und <expan>diselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                        brief <expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> in und wirb von
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan>, als die stallung gen den von Hanaw
                                <expan>yeczund<ex>en</ex></expan>
<app>
<note><q type="date">auf sant Michels tag</q>29.09.1410</note>
</app> awsgeet. Und bitt sie, daz sie darczü beholffen sein, daz dieselb
                        sache <expan>leng<ex>er</ex></expan> bestellet
                        <expan>w<ex>er</ex>de</expan>, und so, das ye <expan>leng<ex>er</ex></expan>
                        gesein möcht, ye pesser uns dewchte. Möht es <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan>
                        nicht <add>lenger</add> gesein, daz es doch auf
                        <app><note><q type="date"><expan>weihenacht<ex>e</ex>n</expan></q>25.12.1410</note></app>
<expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> ee <app><note><q type="date">auf sant <expan>Mert<ex>ein</ex></expan></q>11.11.1410</note></app>
                        bestellet würd. Und lazz dir das <expan>bevolh<ex>e</ex>n</expan> sein. Auch
                        solt du danyden <expan>beleib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> bis
                            <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> tag ein end nem.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
